## Step 7: Final Checks

Before opening the PR, run the full quality gauntlet:

```bash
# Format and lint
ruff format .
ruff check --fix .

# Run all unit tests
pytest tests/unit -x --timeout=60

# Check for any uncommitted changes
git status
```

If there are uncommitted changes (e.g. from lint fixes), commit them:
```bash
git add -A
git commit -m "<ticket-id>: lint and format fixes"
```

